# 🍱 Food Delivery App

This is a mobile UI/UX design project for a food delivery app consisting of 3 screens. The app focuses on user-friendly navigation and an easy ordering experience. Designed with a clean layout to help users browse food items, view details, and place orders efficiently.

## 📱 Screens

- Home Screen (featured food & categories)
- Menu/Product Details Screen
- Cart/Checkout Screen

## 🛠️ Tools Used

- Figma

